# .dockerignore for the API image.
#
# NOTE ON CONTEXT: the API image is built from the PARENT directory (so the
# mimik-contracts / mimik-knowledge siblings are visible). Docker reads the
# .dockerignore at the CONTEXT ROOT, not next to the Dockerfile. Copy this file
# to the parent as `.dockerignore` before building, OR (simpler) let the build
# proceed — the COPY steps are path-scoped so stray files elsewhere in the
# parent are ignored anyway. Patterns below are written to match from the
# parent context (hence the Mimik_Suite/ , mimik-contracts/ prefixes) AND, when
# this file sits at the repo root for a repo-context build, the bare forms.
# See docs/DEPLOY.md.

# ── Python / venv ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/

# ── Node (in case the web tree sits under the same context) ───────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/next-env.d.ts
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Secrets — never ship these into an image layer ────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/credentials*
**/secure repo/
**/secure_repo/

# ── Runtime / generated data ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/var/
**/_archive/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/*.egg-info/

# ── VCS / editor / OS cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.github/
**/.DS_Store
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# ── Docs / tests not needed at runtime (keep migrations!) ─────────────────────
**/docs/
**/tests/
